1
00:00:06,600 --> 00:00:11,537
=The Moment I Met You=

2
00:00:11,537 --> 00:00:14,962
=Episode 38=

3
00:00:15,960 --> 00:00:18,640
My grandfather and Luo Shixun

4
00:00:19,239 --> 00:00:21,760
became sworn brothers
over the Gold-Threaded Armor case.

5
00:00:22,280 --> 00:00:23,399
After their pact,

6
00:00:23,559 --> 00:00:25,559
Luo Shixun was prepared
to hand the armor over.

7
00:00:25,879 --> 00:00:27,280
It was meant to be an honorable act.

8
00:00:27,920 --> 00:00:30,879
But you found
a vulnerability to exploit.

9
00:00:32,119 --> 00:00:32,840
Commissioner.

10
00:00:33,000 --> 00:00:35,560
- You found out Luo Shixun had stolen credit
- Commissioner, I found the Gold-Threaded Armor.

11
00:00:35,560 --> 00:00:38,039
from Chu Zhongtian for finding
the Gold-Threaded Armor.

12
00:00:38,039 --> 00:00:39,162
(Young Liu Sanhuai)
He used that lie to climb the ranks.

13
00:00:40,280 --> 00:00:41,039
Impressive.

14
00:00:43,039 --> 00:00:44,280
(You used that as blackmail,)

15
00:00:44,759 --> 00:00:47,759
(forcing Luo Shixun to hunt down
the Gold and Silver Sacred Tokens.)

16
00:00:52,399 --> 00:00:53,439
(But fate had other plans.)

17
00:00:54,119 --> 00:00:56,560
(Luo Shixun only managed
to recover the Gold Sacred Token.)

18
00:00:56,560 --> 00:00:57,479
And the other?

19
00:00:57,479 --> 00:00:59,960
- (The other one was snatched by Dongfang Qing.)
- The other one was missing.

20
00:00:59,960 --> 00:01:00,520
Useless.

21
00:01:00,520 --> 00:01:02,330
(It vanished
from the Martial World entirely.)

22
00:01:03,240 --> 00:01:05,519
For thirty years,
my grandfather and my father

23
00:01:05,519 --> 00:01:08,040
searched desperately
for the truth about those tokens.

24
00:01:08,187 --> 00:01:10,587
Terrified of being exposed,

25
00:01:10,920 --> 00:01:12,560
you hid behind Luo Shixun.

26
00:01:12,680 --> 00:01:14,200
You pretended to help him

27
00:01:14,519 --> 00:01:16,439
reach the rank of Commissioner.

28
00:01:16,525 --> 00:01:18,764
While you played the part

29
00:01:18,879 --> 00:01:20,200
of a lowly Director of Personnel.

30
00:01:21,040 --> 00:01:23,200
In secret, you were
still hunting for Dongfang Qing

31
00:01:23,200 --> 00:01:24,640
and the missing Sacred Token.

32
00:01:25,799 --> 00:01:26,799
Well,

33
00:01:26,799 --> 00:01:30,560
the face of an operation
is always a target.

34
00:01:30,560 --> 00:01:32,959
It's much safer to stay in the shadows.

35
00:01:34,519 --> 00:01:35,719
When Buyu and I fell in love,

36
00:01:36,040 --> 00:01:38,000
you quickly saw through my identity.

37
00:01:38,200 --> 00:01:40,400
You realized it was another opportunity.

38
00:01:40,799 --> 00:01:43,920
Luo Shixun's ambition
was spiraling out of control.

39
00:01:44,079 --> 00:01:46,480
He was losing respect
for the man who made him.

40
00:01:46,719 --> 00:01:48,719
So you decided to eliminate him as well.

41
00:01:49,560 --> 00:01:52,560
You used the deaths of our fathers

42
00:01:52,690 --> 00:01:54,159
to drive a wedge between me and Buyu.

43
00:01:54,879 --> 00:01:56,200
You forced me to flee to Xichuan

44
00:01:56,640 --> 00:01:58,400
just to dig into Luo Shixun's past.

45
00:01:59,879 --> 00:02:01,959
Some people, unfortunately,

46
00:02:01,959 --> 00:02:04,719
simply don't know their place.

47
00:02:05,040 --> 00:02:07,280
So, making Yue Lun the Commissioner

48
00:02:07,640 --> 00:02:08,680
was your plan all along?

49
00:02:10,879 --> 00:02:12,240
He's an honest man.

50
00:02:12,639 --> 00:02:15,840
Certainly easier to control
than Luo Shixun.

51
00:02:16,199 --> 00:02:17,800
You're as cunning as they come.

52
00:02:18,599 --> 00:02:19,919
You used our grief

53
00:02:20,199 --> 00:02:22,199
to eliminate
a disobedient pawn like Luo Shixun.

54
00:02:22,639 --> 00:02:23,479
And now,

55
00:02:23,879 --> 00:02:25,719
with both tokens in your hands,

56
00:02:26,120 --> 00:02:27,790
you have the Gate Bureau
and the Ministry

57
00:02:27,800 --> 00:02:29,039
right where you want them.

58
00:02:30,000 --> 00:02:30,719
Director Liu,

59
00:02:31,199 --> 00:02:32,840
you want to rule

60
00:02:34,120 --> 00:02:35,639
the light and the dark.

61
00:02:35,879 --> 00:02:37,240
I'm bringing you in!

62
00:02:38,062 --> 00:02:41,162
(Great Virtue)

63
00:02:44,759 --> 00:02:45,719
Mao Buyu,

64
00:02:46,560 --> 00:02:47,960
in my original plan,

65
00:02:48,319 --> 00:02:50,319
Yue Lun was only a placeholder.

66
00:02:51,199 --> 00:02:52,840
The next Commissioner

67
00:02:52,840 --> 00:02:53,840
was meant to be you,

68
00:02:54,080 --> 00:02:55,719
or perhaps Luo Wushuang.

69
00:02:56,439 --> 00:02:58,120
Strictly speaking,

70
00:02:58,560 --> 00:03:00,280
I always preferred you.

71
00:03:02,000 --> 00:03:05,520
But you're an Embroidered Guard,

72
00:03:06,039 --> 00:03:07,879
sent here specifically to investigate me.

73
00:03:09,840 --> 00:03:14,400
I suppose I have no choice
but to finish you both off.

74
00:03:34,199 --> 00:03:35,520
So, you know martial arts.

75
00:03:37,159 --> 00:03:39,159
Who ever said I didn't?

76
00:03:52,159 --> 00:03:54,039
He's calculating
and his technique is lethal.

77
00:03:54,120 --> 00:03:54,879
Be careful!

78
00:04:37,279 --> 00:04:38,000
Five of you?

79
00:04:38,319 --> 00:04:39,959
I could take ten of you,

80
00:04:40,360 --> 00:04:41,879
and you still wouldn't
stand a chance.

81
00:05:08,639 --> 00:05:09,199
My dear!

82
00:06:06,040 --> 00:06:06,759
Wushuang!

83
00:06:10,720 --> 00:06:11,399
My dear!

84
00:06:13,600 --> 00:06:14,560
Chang, are you alright?

85
00:06:16,480 --> 00:06:17,720
I have the Sacred Token.

86
00:06:20,962 --> 00:06:23,025
(Token)

87
00:06:23,920 --> 00:06:25,000
Finally, it's ours.

88
00:06:28,480 --> 00:06:29,240
Commander Mao.

89
00:06:29,600 --> 00:06:31,150
As an officer of the Embroidered Guard,

90
00:06:31,360 --> 00:06:33,720
are you really going to let them
walk away with those?

91
00:06:42,519 --> 00:06:43,199
Chang.

92
00:07:13,560 --> 00:07:14,199
Not so fast.

93
00:07:19,675 --> 00:07:21,839
(Great Virtue)

94
00:07:21,839 --> 00:07:23,120
This belongs to the Chu family.

95
00:07:23,399 --> 00:07:24,920
But it's vital evidence for the case.

96
00:07:25,012 --> 00:07:26,492
What does that have to do with us?

97
00:07:47,399 --> 00:07:48,000
Let's go.

98
00:07:50,475 --> 00:07:51,662
(Great Virtue)

99
00:07:54,079 --> 00:07:54,800
(Yunchang.)

100
00:07:55,839 --> 00:07:56,920
(Why are you running?)

101
00:07:57,959 --> 00:07:59,639
(Did you come back for me)

102
00:08:00,040 --> 00:08:01,519
(or the Sacred Token?)

103
00:08:02,875 --> 00:08:03,675
They're gone.

104
00:08:04,000 --> 00:08:04,990
Should we go after them?

105
00:08:08,199 --> 00:08:10,000
No. I will answer to the Emperor myself.

106
00:08:13,639 --> 00:08:14,319
Yu.

107
00:08:14,759 --> 00:08:15,360
Sister.

108
00:08:16,279 --> 00:08:17,319
Liu Sanhuai is dead.

109
00:08:17,959 --> 00:08:20,240
Our father has finally been avenged.

110
00:09:11,440 --> 00:09:13,559
I pay my respects to Your Majesty.

111
00:09:13,919 --> 00:09:15,720
Long live Your Majesty.

112
00:09:21,279 --> 00:09:22,000
You may rise.

113
00:09:28,480 --> 00:09:31,679
Your father only agreed to serve me

114
00:09:32,159 --> 00:09:34,080
to ensure your safety.

115
00:09:34,519 --> 00:09:36,480
I always suspected

116
00:09:36,799 --> 00:09:39,879
that Luo Shixun's control
of the Gate Bureau was suspicious.

117
00:09:40,360 --> 00:09:43,399
However, I lacked the evidence to act.

118
00:09:44,080 --> 00:09:46,600
So, I sent Mao Buyu
to investigate undercover.

119
00:09:46,960 --> 00:09:47,960
I didn't expect you two

120
00:09:48,919 --> 00:09:50,320
to fall in love,

121
00:09:50,480 --> 00:09:53,000
let alone stumble into
cracking such a case.

122
00:09:53,720 --> 00:09:55,639
It's quite a remarkable story.

123
00:09:56,639 --> 00:09:57,639
So Your Majesty

124
00:09:57,639 --> 00:09:59,399
has known the truth from the start.

125
00:09:59,770 --> 00:10:00,840
Your Majesty is truly wise.

126
00:10:02,279 --> 00:10:04,440
Spare me the flattery.

127
00:10:04,559 --> 00:10:05,919
I've heard quite enough of it.

128
00:10:09,519 --> 00:10:10,440
I have failed you.

129
00:10:11,080 --> 00:10:13,480
I was unable to return
the Sacred Token to Your Majesty.

130
00:10:14,039 --> 00:10:15,159
I beg for your forgiveness.

131
00:10:15,559 --> 00:10:18,039
The matter of the Sacred Token is closed.

132
00:10:19,080 --> 00:10:20,279
Let us not speak of it again.

133
00:10:20,799 --> 00:10:21,720
Could it be Chang?

134
00:10:22,799 --> 00:10:23,399
Your Majesty...

135
00:10:23,519 --> 00:10:24,279
Mao Buyu.

136
00:10:24,679 --> 00:10:25,759
You've done well.

137
00:10:26,080 --> 00:10:27,790
Return to
the Northern Constabulary Office.

138
00:10:27,960 --> 00:10:30,759
You are promoted to Vice Commissioner
of the Embroidered Guard.

139
00:10:33,840 --> 00:10:35,240
I am unworthy of such an honor.

140
00:10:35,679 --> 00:10:37,919
I wish only to remain
a constable in the Gate Bureau.

141
00:10:38,320 --> 00:10:39,519
I ask for your blessing.

142
00:10:48,120 --> 00:10:48,720
Move!

143
00:10:48,987 --> 00:10:50,200
(Six months later)

144
00:10:50,200 --> 00:10:50,919
Keep moving!

145
00:10:51,000 --> 00:10:52,120
- Go!
- Move it!

146
00:10:52,440 --> 00:10:53,279
Keep up!

147
00:10:53,840 --> 00:10:54,600
Stop dawdling!

148
00:10:55,120 --> 00:10:55,720
Hurry!

149
00:10:55,919 --> 00:10:56,559
Yu!

150
00:10:56,919 --> 00:10:58,679
Capturing the Three Bandits of the North

151
00:10:58,759 --> 00:10:59,679
has made you famous.

152
00:11:00,039 --> 00:11:02,190
Once the interrogation is done,
report to the Ministry of Justice.

153
00:11:04,639 --> 00:11:05,279
Move!

154
00:11:07,440 --> 00:11:08,120
Yu.

155
00:11:08,679 --> 00:11:10,759
You've caught so many thieves
these past six months,

156
00:11:10,919 --> 00:11:12,360
yet you still seem so miserable.

157
00:11:13,000 --> 00:11:13,720
I know.

158
00:11:14,159 --> 00:11:16,000
Ever since Yunchang
went to see the Emperor,

159
00:11:16,480 --> 00:11:17,799
there hasn't been a word from her.

160
00:11:18,360 --> 00:11:19,360
That's why, isn't it?

161
00:11:20,000 --> 00:11:21,039
But the way I see it,

162
00:11:21,360 --> 00:11:23,320
she clearly wants
nothing more to do with us.

163
00:11:23,700 --> 00:11:24,879
You shouldn't stay so devoted.

164
00:11:24,879 --> 00:11:25,480
Sister.

165
00:11:26,639 --> 00:11:28,180
I don't plan on staying in the Capital.

166
00:11:28,279 --> 00:11:28,879
What?

167
00:11:30,279 --> 00:11:31,440
I've applied

168
00:11:32,039 --> 00:11:33,960
for a transfer to the Nanjing Gate Bureau

169
00:11:35,159 --> 00:11:36,120
as their Commissioner.

170
00:11:38,240 --> 00:11:41,080
From now on, I'll leave everything here
to you, Wushuang, and Gao Shun.

171
00:11:42,440 --> 00:11:43,279
I'm counting on you.

172
00:11:43,325 --> 00:11:46,875
(Personnel Corps)

173
00:11:48,960 --> 00:11:50,360
Exquisite paintings and calligraphy!

174
00:11:50,400 --> 00:11:51,150
(Nanjing)

175
00:11:51,200 --> 00:11:52,120
Care for a look?

176
00:11:53,120 --> 00:11:55,559
Trinkets and curios! Come see!

177
00:11:59,675 --> 00:12:01,450
(The Meeting Flower Shop)

178
00:12:01,480 --> 00:12:02,799
Was this flower shop here before?

179
00:12:03,120 --> 00:12:04,840
Sir, it just opened.

180
00:12:05,399 --> 00:12:06,200
Take a look inside.

181
00:12:07,050 --> 00:12:07,562
(The Meeting Flower Shop)

182
00:12:07,600 --> 00:12:08,440
Please, come in!

183
00:12:29,900 --> 00:12:33,862
♪Donning a mask to hide my heart♪

184
00:12:33,987 --> 00:12:37,475
♪Playing a part with a hollow smile♪

185
00:12:38,100 --> 00:12:42,050
♪Pitted against each other,
neither of us gives in♪

186
00:12:42,100 --> 00:12:45,737
♪One is cold as ice,
the other is burning like fire♪

187
00:12:47,120 --> 00:12:49,190
I went to the temple
and got this protection charm.

188
00:12:49,679 --> 00:12:52,360
You spend every day fighting criminals.

189
00:12:52,679 --> 00:12:54,279
I can't help but worry about you.

190
00:12:54,325 --> 00:12:57,737
♪I long for it so much,
I crave to return♪

191
00:12:57,950 --> 00:13:01,437
♪To the moment we first met♪

192
00:13:01,519 --> 00:13:02,159
See you.

193
00:13:02,159 --> 00:13:05,896
♪Casting aside all obsession
just to be with you♪

194
00:13:05,987 --> 00:13:09,820
♪Despite countless ordeals♪

195
00:13:10,000 --> 00:13:13,762
♪I can't untie the knot in your heart♪

196
00:13:14,025 --> 00:13:16,025
♪I end up creating another knot instead♪

197
00:13:16,039 --> 00:13:16,720
Sir.

198
00:13:20,559 --> 00:13:21,440
Do you need flowers?

199
00:13:22,037 --> 00:13:25,887
♪But I'll spend my life
keeping you safe♪

200
00:13:26,000 --> 00:13:30,425
♪Lies and vows,
let them stay in the past♪

201
00:13:30,450 --> 00:13:37,900
♪Let's return to when we first met♪

202
00:13:42,212 --> 00:13:45,487
♪Grudges and regrets
are like strong wine♪

203
00:13:45,525 --> 00:13:48,400
♪Drink it down and let it go♪

204
00:13:48,900 --> 00:13:54,618
♪An empty cup for our love and hate♪

205
00:13:55,800 --> 00:13:59,120
♪Tears blur a fate I can't control♪

206
00:13:59,250 --> 00:14:02,170
♪Let's drink until dawn♪

207
00:14:03,338 --> 00:14:08,578
♪Behind this mask, I'll never lie♪

208
00:14:09,800 --> 00:14:12,193
♪Every reunion feels like the first♪

209
00:14:12,193 --> 00:14:15,843
♪This hidden smile will never fade♪

210
00:14:15,912 --> 00:14:19,402
♪One heart, standing by your side♪

211
00:14:19,500 --> 00:14:22,475
♪To the ends of time♪

212
00:14:22,475 --> 00:14:25,850
♪The moon traces your face♪

213
00:14:26,037 --> 00:14:29,625
♪Draped in clouds, you fill my heart♪

214
00:14:29,625 --> 00:14:35,865
♪To find you
and keep our promise forever♪

215
00:14:36,200 --> 00:14:39,415
♪A silent prayer in my soul♪

216
00:14:39,700 --> 00:14:43,238
♪Carrying my vow beneath the moon♪

217
00:14:43,525 --> 00:14:46,550
♪Hoping we never drift apart again♪

218
00:14:46,550 --> 00:14:49,650
♪On our way to forever♪

219
00:14:49,650 --> 00:14:53,500
♪The moon traces your face♪

220
00:14:53,500 --> 00:14:56,860
♪Draped in clouds, you fill my heart♪

221
00:14:57,050 --> 00:15:03,010
♪To find you
and keep our promise forever♪

222
00:15:04,087 --> 00:15:13,727
♪Just to be with you♪
